briefdescription.para: Be sure to use base.OnAwake() when overriding.

detaileddescription.para: This is called when the NetObject runs Awake(). All code that depends on the NetObj being initialized should use this rather than Awake();

briefdescription.para: Owner changes can get dicey, this reapplies the state after an owner change.

memberdef.argsstring: (ObjState newState, ObjState previousState, Transform attachmentTransform, Mount attachTo=null, bool isReady=true)
memberdef.name: OnStateChange
